text: Roman Přikryl (born February 11, 1995) is a Czech professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing for HC Plzeň of the Czech Extraliga. Přikryl made his Czech Extraliga debut playing with HC Plzeň during the 2014-15 Czech Extraliga season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:HC Plzeň players Category:Czech ice hockey forwards Category:Sportspeople from Plzeň
